{"tid":12814,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"交不到女朋友 男在新年首日憤而自宮","createTime":"2016-11-29T21:45:41.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T23:31:45.000Z","uid":12709,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a228c736f812589a549281654437781c24d9c9b0","tid":12814,"uid":12709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T21:45:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20160106/640_ffc4e2920718c00173c4aee244a86662.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftwimg.edgesuite.net%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20160106%2F640_ffc4e2920718c00173c4aee244a86662.jpg&d=Cxq6fU51OcuVLB8gp8NaVwT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=eac74f01\" target=\"_blank\">http://twimg.edgesuite.net/images/ReNews/20160106/640_ffc4e2920718c00173c4aee244a86662.jpg</a><br />\n肯亞一名25歲男子奇摩訶(Leonard Kimotho)就在1月1日新年這天，正當大家歡天喜地慶祝2016年到來時，他卻選擇在這天自宮。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n據奈及利亞《PULSE》網站報導，奇摩訶因為遲遲交不到女朋友，又在跨年前被一名女子拒絕，他自認為「我的陰莖已經無用武之地」，於是選擇在新年的第一天自宮。奇摩訶的家人表示，家人都不知道奇摩訶有這樣的打算和行動，當看到他下體滿身血衝回家時，才發現事態不妙。家人後來找來村裡首長幫忙，並將奇摩訶送醫。<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n醫師表示會盡全力幫奇摩訶把「寶貝」接回去，但也表示他的情況並不樂觀。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）"},{"pid":"fa6f4d3c7573d7db6476b418fab3fe1b82509b55","tid":12814,"uid":28111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:31:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}